data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
See, the thing is: I had made a compromise when I said I'd work on this instead of another project when my PC was stolen...
I told you guys that I'd ship the first version with less features that would consume more time to implement compared to simpler versions that just work.
This is true for using the Timeline with the mouse, and probably other things. Originally, the Timeline was just gonna be a list of keyframes, not intuitive at all, but I decided to go ahead and make a graphic timeline anyway. Let me know of other improvements if you want them!
I hope to get mouse and more working in a future version!
